        <h1>About Engineering Exercise</h1>

        <p>
          Engineering Exercise is a YouTube channel built on a simple idea:
          <strong>the best way to understand something deeply is to exercise it</strong> —
          to work through it step by step, under real constraints, with honest feedback.
        </p>

        <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
        <p>
          Every video is structured like a training session. A problem is introduced,
          a method is applied, and the result is analyzed — no hand-waving, no
          skipping steps. Topics range from system design to algorithm analysis to
          real-world engineering tradeoffs.
        </p>

